{"id": "ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs", "rating": 4.5, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 387, "displayName": {"text": "KamadoSushi (Omakase)", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Sushi, seasonal sashimi & teriyaki in a relaxed yet modern dining room with tables & bar seating.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twRVdscHZaV0ZZZVU1YU9HdHJXa0p3ZVRsWFpIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here specifically for the Kohada and it was beyond expectations! Kohada is kinda hard to find around Bay Area and not many sushi restaurants have them. So I was super grateful to be able to find it here.\n\nI rly enjoyed each piece of nigiri, from the sushi rice, to the amount of wasabi being applied to each piece, to the quality of the fish. Owner/taisho was from Japan, and knows the proper technique. Waiter was so nice!!! Gave us such good suggestions for picking the right fish. Owners told us fish are all overnight shipped from Japan and they will rotate based on seasonal availability to ensure the best quality, And I can def tell that from the taste!\n\nThe price is very reasonable as well. I had an amazing experience and will def come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here specifically for the Kohada and it was beyond expectations! Kohada is kinda hard to find around Bay Area and not many sushi restaurants have them. So I was super grateful to be able to find it here.\n\nI rly enjoyed each piece of nigiri, from the sushi rice, to the amount of wasabi being applied to each piece, to the quality of the fish. Owner/taisho was from Japan, and knows the proper technique. Waiter was so nice!!! Gave us such good suggestions for picking the right fish. Owners told us fish are all overnight shipped from Japan and they will rotate based on seasonal availability to ensure the best quality, And I can def tell that from the taste!\n\nThe price is very reasonable as well. I had an amazing experience and will def come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amanda Liu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115691174480067777186/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlqt2MM9K2acm6l1JCEA6VHBYkZYtP4pfMc1qQJJVpOfPBP3cHug=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-16T05:10:56.259869520Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twRVdscHZaV0ZZZVU1YU9HdHJXa0p3ZVRsWFpIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twRVdscHZaV0ZZZVU1YU9HdHJXa0p3ZVRsWFpIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea68d730255:0xfb36f3c2a8c7c68d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJdU5qRVVREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We are so lucky to have this gem in our neighborhood. Jin is an incredible chef, overseeing daily fresh fish flown in from Japan, his omakase is comparable to the Michelin sushi spots in sf. … but for a neighborhood price with neighborhood feel.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We are so lucky to have this gem in our neighborhood. Jin is an incredible chef, overseeing daily fresh fish flown in from Japan, his omakase is comparable to the Michelin sushi spots in sf. … but for a neighborhood price with neighborhood feel.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Samantha Good", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107158290271594498324/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhweZ-hyadQpUTcXMiwXnmjkjf4lSQd51BaCRuvEsDevYl0M4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-03-30T03:54:16.630861Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJdU5qRVVREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJdU5qRVVREAE!2m1!1s0x80857ea68d730255:0xfb36f3c2a8c7c68d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURub1BQSUNnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "A small chirashi bowl with fewer than 10 pieces of sashimi costs $30, the same as the Unagi Don. While both dishes tasted good, they were on the expensive side. Salmon and Hirame nigiris are about the average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A small chirashi bowl with fewer than 10 pieces of sashimi costs $30, the same as the Unagi Don. While both dishes tasted good, they were on the expensive side. Salmon and Hirame nigiris are about the average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hannah Jin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106886643289463162646/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-Vp4dRIlE0ESrjzGTS6DlEU_p8wHTjZboJ53irljTEwTPQc6q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2024-10-02T02:59:30.079916Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURub1BQSUNnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURub1BQSUNnEAE!2m1!1s0x80857ea68d730255:0xfb36f3c2a8c7c68d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNxd3RLZzRRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "After more than a year of lock-down, we celebrated social liberation with a fabulous sushi dinner sitting at the sushi bar watching the sushi master preparing \"Omakase\" (chief's choice) assortment of the most delicious and beautifully presented succulent servings of fresh fish east of Japan, all while savoring glasses of fragrant chilled sake from a 1800 ml bottle of Konteki Tears of Dawn Daiginjo - absolutely heaven on earth!  Not cheap, but worth every penny spent!  In short, the best sushi in the Bay Area!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "After more than a year of lock-down, we celebrated social liberation with a fabulous sushi dinner sitting at the sushi bar watching the sushi master preparing \"Omakase\" (chief's choice) assortment of the most delicious and beautifully presented succulent servings of fresh fish east of Japan, all while savoring glasses of fragrant chilled sake from a 1800 ml bottle of Konteki Tears of Dawn Daiginjo - absolutely heaven on earth!  Not cheap, but worth every penny spent!  In short, the best sushi in the Bay Area!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Douglas Unsworth", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104429722035888906114/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHbNZL7wd2j1-cEEAGO3ksSy_Drp3rBoP_A0WEAyjO6rh0qQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2021-05-31T17:21:15.287402Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNxd3RLZzRRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNxd3RLZzRRRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857ea68d730255:0xfb36f3c2a8c7c68d"}, {"name": "places/ChIJVQJzjaZ-hYARjcbHqMLzNvs/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWbFdEQTJWelJFY0d4U1pXaHlPR2cwWmkxM01HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Good access to the variety of seasonal fish straight from Japan. We had an ala carte nigiri selection from the daily menu behind the counter. Perfect experience where the fish is prepared well and sake just completed the satisfying meal.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Good access to the variety of seasonal fish straight from Japan. We had an ala carte nigiri selection from the daily menu behind the counter. Perfect experience where the fish is 